csw.services.alarms

Class AlarmModel.HealthStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • csw.services.alarms.AlarmModel.HealthStatus
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, scala.Equals, scala.Product
    Enclosing class:
    AlarmModel

    public static class AlarmModel.HealthStatus
extends java.lang.Object
implements scala.Product, scala.Serializable
    Combines an alarm key (which may use wildcards to match a system, subsystem or component) with a health value, which is calculated from all the alarms matching the given alarm key.

    param: timestamp a timestamp for the health event param: key an alarm key matching all alarms for the system, a subsystem or component param: health the total health, calculated from the severity values of all the alarms matching the key
